dataset
Class Dataset

java.lang.Object
  dataset.Dataset
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Dataset
extends Object
implements Serializable

Datasets are used by Neural Networks. They gathered together Samples, which are simply two vectors : one with the Neural Network input values, the other with the output values.
